room_title: Escape room "Dinner for Two" by Waco Escape Rooms in Waco
room_description: You deserve a nice meal out with someone special. So you think. Your waiter snaps and you find yourself alone with nobody but your partner and nothing but a menu to keep you company. Your surrounding may seem to be a lovely cafe - but your private dining room is also the ultimate puzzle box! Can you find the clues you need to solve it and escape?
